            <title>Galaxy Watch7 Ultra 网上曝光，表身采用外方内圆设计</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/galaxy-watch7-ultra-cad-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=galaxy-watch7-ultra-cad-leaked</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/galaxy-watch7-ultra-cad-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:00:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Watch7 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1238277</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前有报导指 Galaxy Watch7 系列将配备升级的处理器，电池寿命得以延长，并且新增血糖监测功能，但无法确认这些改变是对应全个 Galaxy Watch7 系列，还是只有 Ultra 版本获得升级。在 Galaxy Watch7 传闻在 7 月的 Galaxy Unpacked 活动发表前，有爆料人公开了声称是 Galaxy Watch7 Ultra 的设计图。</p><p><span id="more-1238277"></span></p><p>假如网上流传的图片属实，这款今年新增的 Ultra 型号手表，将会采用外方内圆的设计，表壳本身呈方形，边缘为椭圆形，而屏幕和旋转表圈则保持圆形。这批 Galaxy Watch7 Ultra 设计图还展示了以往所没有的全新圆形按钮，设于常见的电源和返回按钮旁边，爆料者并没有进一步透露新按钮的具体功能。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1238290" rel="attachment wp-att-1238290"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1238290" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/05274b-694x390.jpg" alt="Samsung Galaxy Watch7 Ultra" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/05274b-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/05274b.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>有指表面屏幕尺寸保持不变，与现时 Watch6 Classic 的 1.5 吋相同，并符合 47 毫米的标准。设计图还显示 Galaxy Watch7 Ultra 表壳的另一边有比以往更大的扬声器格栅，背部感应器亦用上新的排列，而手表表带与表身更无缝结合。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/samsung_is_readying_a_galaxy_watch7_ultra_leaked_renders_suggest-news-62998.php">gsmarena</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/19/samsung-tv-2024/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung TV 2024 全电视系列现场评测，加入 AI 让 8K 解像度更实用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/16/samsung-galaxy-a55-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Samsung Galaxy A55　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/25/ifixit-samsung-repair-relationship-ends/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iFixit 解除与 Samsung 合作关系　认为 Samsung 无意降低维修门槛</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/galaxy-watch7-ultra-cad-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/">Galaxy Watch7 Ultra 网上曝光，表身采用外方内圆设计</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
